    dc:creator "Rameshkumar, A.; Noyes, J. S.; Poorani, J.; Chong, J. H." ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "Description of a new species of Anagyrus Howard (Hymenoptera: Chalcidoidea: Encyrtidae), a promising biological control agent of the invasive Madeira mealybug, Phenacoccus madeirensis Green (Hemiptera: Sternorrhyncha: Pseudococcidae)" ;
